dc_title_s: High Resolution Orthoimagery, Polk and Beltrami Counties, MN, Spring 2014: Minnesota
dc_description_s: This dataset contains leaf-off 4-band red, green, blue, infrared (RGBI) digital orthophoto imagery produced at 30-centimeter (approximately one-foot) resolution from new aerial photography captured in Spring 2014. The imagery covers Polk and Beltrami counties in northwestern Minnesota. This metadata record was created by the Minnesota Geospatial Information Office (MnGeo) using information supplied by Quantum Spatial Inc.
dc_creator_sm: Polk County; Beltrami County; Quantum Spatial, Inc.
